# ⚙️ Features

## ✅ 1. Process Reports

* Reads ZIP files from a folder
* Extracts and processes latest or multiple reports

---

## ✅ 2. Convert to Excel

* Extracts:

  * Transaction data
  * Summary statistics
* Saves into structured Excel

---

## ✅ 3. Compare Reports

* Compare latest **N reports**
* Adds:

| Feature          | Description                           |
| ---------------- | ------------------------------------- |
| Multi-file merge | Combine reports                       |
| Trend column     | ⬆ Improved / ⬇ Degraded / ➖ No Change |

---

## ✅ 4. Email Integration (Outlook)

* Send reports directly via Outlook
* Supports:

  * Single recipient
  * Multiple recipients
  * Comparison reports

