# 🧠 Prompt-Based Commands

## 📊 Basic Commands

### 👉 Get latest report

```
get latest lre report
```

---

### 👉 Process specific path

```
process report from C:\Ahold\Projects\BIDM\Result
```

---

### 👉 Process multiple reports

```
process latest 3 reports
```

---

### 👉 Process all reports

```
process result of all files
```

---

## 📈 Comparison Commands

### 👉 Compare reports

```
compare latest 2 reports
```

---

### 👉 Compare multiple

```
compare latest 3 reports
```

---

## 📧 Email Commands

### 👉 Send latest report

```
send latest report to abc@company.com
```

---

### 👉 Send to multiple users

```
send latest report to abc@company.com, xyz@company.com
```

---

### 👉 Compare + Email

```
compare latest 2 reports and email to abc@company.com, xyz@company.com
```

---

### 👉 Process + Email

```
process latest 3 reports and send to team@company.com
```

